entry.string: This may take a moment. Thank you for your patience.
entry.translation: Thees mey teke-a a mument. Um de hur de hur de hur. Thunk yuoo fur yuoor peteeence-a.

entry.string: You already have an installed database.
entry.translation: Yuoo elreedy hefe-a un instelled detebese-a.

entry.string: If you continue your previous data will be overwritten.
entry.translation: Iff yuoo cunteenooe-a yuoor prefeeuoos deta veell be-a oofervreettee.
